INTRODUCTION: EXPLORING PARALLEL REALITIES MORE DEEPLY

The Purpose of This Transmission

• To explore the concept of parallel realities a little bit more deeply
• To take you through a very specific exercise
• To give you more ability, more facility with the concept of:
  - Connecting to parallel realities
  - Downloading information from a variety of parallel realities
• This transmission is called: THE PARALLELOGRAM

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

THE FUNDAMENTAL PRINCIPLE: EVERYTHING EXISTS ALL AT ONCE

The Foundation

• Everything exists all at once
• Because everything exists all at once, then:
  - What you call the past doesn't really exist anywhere but here and now
  - What you call the future doesn't really exist anywhere but here and now
  - Alongside what you call the present

Past Lives, Future Lives - All Exist NOW

• Even the idea of so-called past lives, so-called future lives
• They all exist NOW in their own frequency domain
• Right alongside the existence of what you know the present to be
• They are just different forms of the present that you may not be at this moment focused on
• Your consciousness may not be exactly aware of them
• But that doesn't mean they don't exist
• It just means they are operating on different frequencies
• And you're simply not tuned to them

