Everything is One Thing

• Because everything is here and now
• Because everything is actually one thing
• Then even what you perceive to be OTHER PEOPLE in your reality
• Even they are actually PARALLEL REFLECTIONS OF YOU from a different point of view

Everything in Your Reality is a Reflection

• Everything in your reality is a reflection of:
  - What you are giving off
  - What you are putting out as the theme you are exploring
• Even though there may be autonomous individuals that are real unto themselves
• And in some sense different from you
• Nevertheless, what you perceive as different individuals in your reality are actually reflections of you in a variety of ways

Different Forms of Relevance

• Some reflections have more or less relevance to you
• Some have different forms of relevance to you as reflections
• Nevertheless, still functioning as actual expressions of parallel versions of you
• Coexisting simultaneously with the identity that you believe yourself to be
• That you are focused as at this particular moment in this particular incarnation

