TOPIC: THE THREE-PART FORMULA OF EXCITEMENT

The Most Important Message

• The message that is the most important message Bashar can possibly deliver:
• Simply the THREE-PART FORMULA:

**Act on your highest passion to the best you are able with absolutely zero insistence on what you think the outcome ought to look like**

That's it.

