WHAT HAPPENS WHEN YOU FOLLOW THE FORMULA

The Kit of Excitement

• When you do that, you activate THE KIT OF EXCITEMENT
• That contains all the tools you need in life

What the Kit Does:

1. **It Becomes the Driving Engine**
   - Propels you through life

2. **It Becomes the Organizing Principle**
   - Through synchronicity
   - Shows you exactly what you need to do
   - In what order
   - And when

3. **It Becomes the Path of Least Resistance**
   - Allows you to flow through your life
   - In an effortless way
   - A joyful way

4. **It Becomes the Path That Connects You**
   - To every expression of your excitement
   - That is relevant for you to express in your life

5. **It Becomes the Reflective Mirror**
   - Reveals to you anything within you that is out of alignment with that excitement
   - So you can identify it and let it go
   - Because it doesn't serve you
   - And add its energy to your overall excitement

6. **It Supports You**
   - In all the ways you need to be supported
   - In order to allow you to continue to act on your excitement to the best of your ability

7. **It Leaves Nothing Relevant Out**
   - It is a complete kit

