TOPIC: SYNCHRONISTIC MARKERS - THE 11:11 PHENOMENON

The Question

• "My son has seen the number 11:11. Every time he turns around on the clock, it's 11:11."

Bashar's Explanation

**Synchronistic Markers:**
• These synchronistic markers, which many of you have
• Sometimes quite often involve the concept of numbers
• Will be symbolic reflections of synchronicity

**What They Mean:**
• When you have that, it's a MARKER
• It's an indication that at that moment you are in the correct energy state
• Fully aligned with your path

**What to Do:**
• STAY IN THAT STATE
• ACT FROM THAT STATE AT THAT MOMENT
• It is showing you that your timing is aligned

